column2: ONION MAGGOT FLY ACTIVITY/WHITE STICKY CARD STUDY 2006 - ELBA
Determine mortality and longevity of lethal effects of spinosad applied to white spheres on onion maggot mortality in the field
White spheres with different doses of spinosad were placed in the field for different times. Sticky cards were placed in the field plots to monitor onion maggot populations
Original data received from Nault lab in December 2018, placed into tabular form in this document in May, 2019.  Onion maggot numbers denote avereage of three sticky cards per plot.
